\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what would there by in the way of toilet facilities and washing facilities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, I couldn't tell you that.
