\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Um, not at all meals, dinner mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did he stop doing it when you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 He stopped when we, when we went to the public house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, we used to have our dinner so late, you see, there, and
, er, sometimes, you see, he would be serving in the bar and that, and we would have dinner and then we'd go and relieve him and he'd come in and have his dinner, you see, because, er, you see, you didn't you didn't close till two o'clock on a Sunday, you
 see, so that, er, it made it so late.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So he didn't eat with you any more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Erm, sometimes he used to if we were late in getting dinner and that, you know, but otherwise it was like a split meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember if you had any books or newspapers or magazines; in any of your homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, yes, daily papers, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What was it, do you remember, or did they change about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, that, er, I think it was the News Chronicle, it was a Liberal paper anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Were your parents Liberals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 My father was a Liberal, and I didn't know that, I didn't know that until I met a man in Oxford, oh, back, let me see, nine years ago.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And he told you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 He told me that my father was a Liberal, and he came from a Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Had you ever wondered what your father was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I always thought he was a Conservative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So he wasn't active in politics then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How did this man, do you think, know that he was a Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Um, well, I couldn't tell you, he, he may have, e
r, he may have belonged to one of the, he may have belonged to one of the branches of the Liberals. Being a publican he may have belonged to, like, erm, the central, central Liberal organization, that used to be in, in, er, er, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid475693\charrsid16135664 Newton}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664  Hall Street at the Reform Club, he may have been a member of the Reform Club.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think as a publican he might have kept his views rather quiet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, I should think so, er, it's the usual thing for, for a publican to be neutral.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You don't remember him talking politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think he voted, though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What about your mother, do you know if she had any views? Of course, she wouldn't have had a vote at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 She didn't have any views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I don't, I don't know what her views were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You yourself, was it within this period that you became interested in the Labour movement, and this sort of thing, or was it later on?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, later one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think that, at that time, people felt that they 
risked their jobs if they voted against their employer's views? Do you remember any cases like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
No, I don't remember any cases, but, er, er, you had to keep your politics quiet, because you never knew where you were, the, the Trade Unions weren't, weren't strong enough at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You were saying you used to have grace..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, wait a minute, I've skipped on from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid475693\charrsid16135664 when }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 you used to get the News Chronicle. Did your parents get any other magazines?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 We used to have Punch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you read that as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Used to have Punch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did they read books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Um, well, I wouldn't say they read a lot of books. Another one that we used to have was John Bull.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did they have books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you read as a child for pleasure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, I used to read quite a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you ever remember reading aloud to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, I can't remember that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you ever remember, when you were a child, a funeral in the family, attending a funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. No, they used to keep the children out of funerals, yes, you, you could, er, you could, er, watch a funeral.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Watch the procession, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. But, er, not out in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So up to this time when you were eighteen you didn't attend a funeral or take part in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 ("No" indicated)
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 To get back to you saying that they used to have grace, where did you have your meals in that house in Hackney?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Um, in the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Was there a front room as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, no, you see, the front room was the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So you always eat in the living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Can you remember what sort of cooking range or stove your mother had at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, it was or-, just an ordinary fire, fire range.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You mean the grate would be out (?) at the side? Yes. And did she have that in the other homes too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Um, yes, even in the public house, er, and that was in the bar, but, er, we never used to used that means of cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What did she used then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Erm, the other one, when we was down in the country, we used to use it on the jack, what they used to call a jack.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Um, it was a mechanism hung, hung from, from the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid475693\charrsid16135664 b}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 oard}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid475693\charrsid16135664 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664  like there'd be a board in front of the fire and that used to be hung}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid475693\charrsid16135664 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
 you used to wind it up with a key and that used to spin the meat round in front of the fire so many times and then it used to come back again, so that all the while that meat was turning backwards and forwards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Like the old-fashioned spit-roasting in a way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, um, it used to be done, really}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid475693\charrsid16135664 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664  what, what they used to term it as a jack.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But she must have had something else as well for boiling and that kind of thing, didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, you used to have trivets on the side of the fire, but you used to do your (..) better and that there, in front of the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 All at about that kind of level, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When you were in King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid475693\charrsid16135664 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 s Sutton, the house of this Lady Brown you mentioned..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 .. having this gas installed ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 ..but your mother didn't have a gas stove there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. No, they weren't in being then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When you were a child, up to eighteen years old, did you have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What members of the family would be present for breakfast? Would you have it as a family meal, or would you take it ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, we'd have it altogether, we would have it altogether and then we used to scurry off to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Your parents would be there for breakfast too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Would it begin at a certain time and finish at a certain time? Would you all sit down together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Oh, we should all sit down together, because, er, er, you see when we came to live in Oxford, the public house opened at six o'clock in the morning.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Quite early, isn't it? It's quite amazing to think of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
You see, you opened, you opened the door at six, if you wasn't opened at six you, you got knocked up, if you overslept, you got knocked up, by the people waiting to come in, because it was, er a rule that, er, that a workman got to work at six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So who would get up, then, to start off?
