\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember any sort of activities they had together, going out anywhere, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, no, no, no, I don't, er, they used to go into Banbury, I know, and they used to
 have one or two, er, friends that they used to go round with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What would they do if they went into Banbury?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, it used to, it usually used to be market days or anything like that, you see, when they used to go into Banbury.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you ever remember your mother going out on her own with a woman friend doing any visiting or excursions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When your father was working in North Parade ..?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That morning job. How old were you when you started doing that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 About twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 About twelve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what time did you have to get to the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Seven thirty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And when you went to school was your work finished for the day then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You didn't do evening papers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. And did you do Sundays as well as Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Saturdays, yes; but not Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And how did you get the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I just went round and applied for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Without an advert you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Just on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you have anything else to do for them or was it just taking the papers round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Just taking the papers, you know, and periodicals and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you collect money for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Can you remember what you were paid? Doesn't matter if you can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 5/- a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 5/- a week. Quite good.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes at that time it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you feel at that time it was a fair wage for what you were doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what did you do with that money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Gave it to me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 All of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did she give you any of it back for yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. If I wanted 6d. or 1/- she used to give it me back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And do you know what she spent it on? If it just went into the general fund or if she put it aside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 She put it aside for clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 For clothes for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Well for clothes for the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 For clothing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 For clothing me brother and sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How did you get on with the people there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you enjoy the work or did you just do it as a routine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well it was like that - you had a job to do and you used to go and do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You didn't think much about whether you enjoyed it or not you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you think it altered your attitude towards school at all. Made you feel differently about it when you were earning money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And then you had this other job which was taking out medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And you did that. What time did you have to be on the job then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Well after school and if he hadn't got anything to take round I never used to have to do anything. And if there was anything to be delivered I simply took it and took it round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. So how long would you perhaps be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh. About and hour, or an hour and half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I used to have a bike for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Supplied by him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Supplied by him. Solid tyres.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Solid tyres did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Funny thought isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And on a Saturday what hours did you work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 Well I used to go in the morning and help him in the shop.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You actually helped serve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not help serve. You know. Clean up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And that. And clean the pallets and anything like that that he was making the medicines up with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And used to take out any orders.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And I used to be there in the morning and in the afternoon.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What sort of time in the morning would you go in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh. Ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And you would go home for your dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
And then go across the road to dinner and then back again about two and if there was any orders to take out I used to take them out or if there wasn't I used to go home and if he had any orders to come he used to come and knock me and ask me to take them.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And what was he like as an employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Very nice indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 He was a self - the shop belonged to him. He was self-employed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Did you come into contact there with any other people to work with or did you just work with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, I just worked with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And what did he pay you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you know if it was more or less?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, it was more than what I got for, for
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 The papers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And how old were you when you took that one up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Did you change because of the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Why did you take up that job then and stop the other one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well it was. You see, at that time there wasn't much to do, not on a Saturday, for children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. And you wanted one with Saturday work for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you do any other part-time jobs before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Those were the only two you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Those were the only two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And with the money you got for the chemist one you did the same, did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Now when you left school what occupation did you take up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 My first job was at Radley College.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What did you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I worked on the staircase. Worked in a house, they use
d to call them house not staircase, at Radley College, with one man and we had two floors. The man would be about, I should say about 26, and we each done one floor each. I should say there was 30 on each floor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Thirty rooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Thirty cubicles. They each had a slipper bath, and you used to make all the beds and do all the sweeping out and serve at table.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you serve at table within the house? Did the boys eat in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, in the hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. The whole school ate together you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Now that's quite a little way from Oxford, isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 We lived in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you go there straight from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How did you find the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well that I couldn't tell you. I think it was through an advert. I remember going over and being interviewed.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Who interviewed you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 One of the masters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Was it the kind of work you felt you wanted to do? Or was it just work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, it wasn't. It was just a start.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And you couldn't pick and choose in those days could you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Would there have been anything else you think you would have particularly liked to do if you'd had the chance then, or had you not any idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I didn't have any idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What was the wage there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I couldn't tell you. No. It was so far back that you don't remember clearly. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How did you feel about the job? How did you find it while you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well it was alright as far as it went. But I didn't stop there. I stopped there for a twelve month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What were your orders? And the person over you, this other man? Did you come into much contact with other people at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Only the other boys in the other houses. Because we used to sleep in a place. All
 the boys slept in one place and the other men used to have to look after the house and they used to have a room in the house, like at the end of a corridor you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And you used to be there too, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. We used to sleep quite apart from the house. There was a place set off for the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How many other boys were there then at the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you spend your spare time doing things with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh roaming around. Catching rabbits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That reminds me of a question I should have asked you earlier on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you ever have, while you were at home, any extra meat from poaching as many families did in those days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. We used to go out with the shoots down at Kings Sutton for partridges, and pheasants, and rook shooting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Did you shoot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. We used to be carriers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You used to be carriers. Your father too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And we used to get so many given us. But as for poaching we never used to have any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 did that stop. There were no more shoots for you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh no more shoots. Not when we came to Oxford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you get along well with the other boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what about the man you worked with on your own floor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 He was very nice. If you hadn't finished he used to come up and help you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Was it hard work, would you say, or light work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well we used to have to empty thirty slipper baths a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 It must have been quite heavy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes they used to hold a lot of water. But making the beds and that was nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What sort of hours were you working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 We used to work all the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And in the afternoons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Sometimes an afternoon off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What about evenings, did you work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well you see, we used to have waiting at table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Did you wait at breakfast, lunch and dinner, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you mix at all, or ever come into friendly contact with the boys themselves
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 They were a race apart were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. They used to speak to you, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember having a conversation with one of them ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you ever think you'd like to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. I took it as a matter of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That they were separate from you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And when you left that one, what did you go on to after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 On munitions at Cowley at Morris's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 It was Morris's then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what were you doing then exactly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Lathe work. On a lathe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And when you were there, were you living at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And how did you find that job? Did you answer an advert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Yes that was when the war broke out. When the war had been on for a twelve-month, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you feel that this was more worthwhile for a job? Did you like it more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. I enjoyed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what were the hours there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Six in the morning, 'til nine at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Very long, weren't they!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 4 and a half pence. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Overtime?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And we used to get so much for every twelve things th
at we done. You know, like a bonus, which used to make our money up very well. Up to round about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8017714 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 5 odd a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Really. That was good money then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what did you do with that money? Did you give any of it to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, I used to give me mother me keep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And have some back for spending?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And how did you get on there with the foreman or people over you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Very well indeed. Had no trouble at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And the other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I meant to
 ask you, when you were back in Radley College, where did you have your own meals. Did you sort of have them in separate quarters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Were you homesick at all while you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 We used to come home every vacation, you see. It was only about thirteen weeks you see and then home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what about weekends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Sometimes at weekends we used to come home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you carry on with that job at Cowley after the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I finished there at... I joined the R.N.A.S. on Boxing Day 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And you worked there up 'til then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I worked there up 'til then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That's right up 'til the end?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And while you were there were you satisfied with what you were doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Or did you sometimes feel you would like to be doing something else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. I was quite content.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You've done very well, really, haven't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. I was quite content.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 While you were there did you belong to any trade union organizations of any kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Was there one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 There was no trade unions at Oxford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 There weren't - none at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not in our trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember feeling at that time that employers and workers had different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not up there. You was all 
one. Freddie Morris, he was like that, that if you got on with your work you was all right; if you didn't well you... 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You weren't all right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You weren't all right. You could take
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You worked for him because he was a good boss.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you come into contact with him personally, there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Oh yes. Yes. I had the highest references that I could get off of him when I went into the forces. Because I went as a boy, you see, and I had to get that from the boss }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 himself}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did he take an interest then in the individual people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. Yes. Oh yes. When I went up for a reference I was speaking to him as though I'm speaking to you now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You didn't have to keep a distance from him like in some sort of jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh no. No. He told me, he said, "I could stop you from going if I want to."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How big was the works there then? And how many people were there employed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 It was only the old Military College that was used.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. For munitions, yes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Because on the other 
side there was nothing at all. That was, it belonged to Maddocks, and that was all vegetables. A proper garden, you know, a kitchen garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So, what about among the workers themselves there, did you feel there were any divisions between them? I mean w
as there any division between craftsmen there and workers or didn't it figure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. It didn't figure. No. you was all doing war work and that was it. You got on with it. There was no dissension among them at all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Would you say that working full t
ime, I'm going back here to when you first started working at Radley, in that other job, do you think it changed your attitude to life? Or how you saw things at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not necessarily.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you come into contact with types of people you had not met before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. Yes in that respect. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 At the college?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. When I was at munitions. You came directly in contact with boys of your own age more, perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Of a kind you had not met before, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 In what way were they different from the boys you had known before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, you see, like playing football and cricket and all that. We used to have our own teams and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you. To do with the works you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you play other clubs and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. We used to play County Barracks.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. We had the L.I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What teams did you play in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I played in first and second at football.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you. And were there any other games you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Cricket. First ones at Cricket.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And had you not had so much sporting activity before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. We started at school, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But they didn't have so much in those days did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But we didn't used to have so much as what we did there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When you started to work did it change your relationships with your mother and father, when you moved away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You still got on the same way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And your brother and sister, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What about Sunday. Did you spend Sunday differently when you were at Radley? Did you go to church there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. We used to go to the Chapel at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 The school Chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Just that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And when you were at the munitions did you ever go to any services then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And your spare time there? Did you go out in the evenings when you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What sort of activities did you attend when you were fifteen and upwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Dancing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You went dancing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How would it be in those days? Would you take a partner, or would you go with a group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I used to go out with a girl who was working at the factory as a matter of fact. Used to take her to the pictures and the like.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You used to go to the pictures?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So you got to know quite a few new boys and girls then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you ever take them home? A girl friend or a boy friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did your parents welcome your taking friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 They didn't mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And when you were out at night, after you came back from Radley, did your parents like to know where you were, or did they consider...

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. They always wanted to know where you was going. And you used to be in by a certain time - before locking up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When was that in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 In by ten, even after a dance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did they like to know who you were with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What about helping with the allotments and things like that? Did you carry on with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. I carried on helping.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You were saying you weren't sure that you would remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Only, you see, I was told at the General Election down at the Town Hall. When I was told then, at the 
General Election, I was sitting next to a radical, and he said "Oh, I know your name", he said. "Well" he said "I know your father". I said "How did you know that?" "Oh," he said "He was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 L}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 iberal." You see, so I had to take it for granted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you know if he ever took part in any sport, or went to races, that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. He used to go to the races. Yes. He used to go to Ascot and that. And also I've been out with him fox hunting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, have you. You mean riding to hounds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, drag.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Drag. And did your mother go to Ascot, too, with him or did he go on his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. They used to make up parties to go to Ascot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Run from the Palace would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did they have a slate club in the public house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I don't quite know what the method is. Do publicans and their wives also join in on that, or do they simply have to keep apart from it?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, the publican runs it. But there's a secretary and a treasurer, appointed by the members, and my fa
ther had nothing at all to do with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 He had no money in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, apart from taking the money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So did your parents themselves at that time you were in Oxford have any savings, you know, for anything in particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 They didn't belong to any thrift clubs or docket clubs or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you know, whether in their other places that they lived, if they belonged to any clubs or slate clubs and such?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That I wouldn't know. I should imagine my father would have done in Kings Sutton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did he go to the pub then, and your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 My mother never used to go there I don't think. My father used to go down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When you were a child, before you left school, who did you play with? Thinking now of the time before {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place
}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} when you were about 11 on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, I used to play with the boys that lived round about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did they all go to the same school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you play with your sister at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Sutton, but not in Oxford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And where did you play with your boy companions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well we used to play in the streets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Anywhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 At Port Meadow, which wasn't very far away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you ever have friends indoors for tea or for playing indoors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 It was outdoor playing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, it was outdoor playing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
And if you got dirty when you played I think you you're your mother would just say she'd expect that from you! Can you remember what games you used to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did they join in the drag hunts at all, the other boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. No. Just one. They used to live at the Church Hall on the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
Street}}Banbury Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, that was next to Gees then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Was that the florist, Gees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. The florist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And there was a boy who lived there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 The boy who lived there. We 
used to, the only time I remember later, about when I was thirteen, we used to play in the Church Hall and go on the parallel bars and horizontal bars and that. That belonged to the Boys Brigade.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Were you members of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, I wasn't old enough. But we used to go in there and go on the parallels.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And that was quite permitted was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What was your parents attitudes to whom you played with? Were they particular about whom you associated with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I think it was their friends' children you know. It was only those that lived round about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
You don't remember you getting friendly with a child, that sometimes happens in families, and your parents for some reason not wanting you to associate with him? That didn't happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember that happening with your sister or brother at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you belong to any youth organizations of any kind, or youth groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You told me how you used to help your father on his allotment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you have any other hobbies or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 past times}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Reading, I used to read a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 In the summer as well as in the winter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well anytime I got hold of a book. And, of course, same as all the boys, I used to do stamp collecting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what sort of books did you read or was it magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. It used to be adventure stories mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Where did you get them from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I used to be able to get hold of them. I don't know how I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Were you in a library?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think other boys passed them on to you and you swopped them around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 They might have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you have quite a few books of your own in your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, not many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You think you got them from some outside sources?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You used to go fishing sometimes, didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you go with other boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Only one. There used to be two of us go. And then, of course, I used to go with my father as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you have a bicycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Not until I was fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. Yes. I used to go about quite a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Were you interested in the countryside at all, looking at buildings and that kind of thing? Natural history and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not buildings. No, we used to go of just where we thought we would you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. I wondered whether you ever went out of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} into the villages in the Cotswolds, or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, we cycled to Kings Sutton many a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you? Quite a way. So you used to go back did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, we went back there. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 To see people was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 While you were still at school did you ever go to cultural activities like concerts and theatres?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Nothing of that kind at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well if we had tuppence a week we thought we was in clover.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You didn't get it regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Just, can I have a penny Mum.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But you couldn't count on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 When your mother was in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, someone used to come in to do sort of rougher work, didn't they, scrubbing in the bar part. Do you remember her }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 having}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
 anybody else at all to look after the family of the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not in Oxford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Was there a woman you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What about in King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 s Sutton, did she ever have any help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you ever remember her being ill, I mean for any period of time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. She used to suffer with stomach ulcers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, did she? Right through your childhood was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 As far bac
k as I can remember when she was in Kings Sutton and then, of course, it gradually got worse when we was in Oxford because she went to nurse my Great Aunt and she was taken ill up there and she went to Guys Hospital. But that was later on though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 After the first World War you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But when she had it up to that time was she laid up, you know, for days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. For a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 As long as that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And how would you manage then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, my sister used to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Even in King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 s Sutton? Would your sister have been old enough 'cos she would only have been about...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
She would have been about thirteen. She would have helped father with it. Of course, there might have been neighbours that came in to help us
. You see on the Estate, because we weren't the only ones on there, you see, there was the coachman and the footman - you see they used to live there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And were your parents on very good terms with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So you think that they would come in and help? And in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, was your mother on friendly terms with the neighbours there too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Only, you see, later on when my sister was married, you see, she used to come and look after her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And would you remember your brother being born? You would have been in Hackney?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. In King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 s Sutton. No. I don't remember him being born, but I can remember him breaking his leg. That was just before we left King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 s Sutton. That was when my father had come to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} to look over, to see the pub, 
which he was going to get. We was playing with him. We stood him on the wall and my sister told him to jump into her arms and she let him go and he broke his leg.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So what did your mother do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well he was taken straight into Banbury and had it fix
ed and you see they brought him back. I can remember that. You know it's those sort of things live in your memory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, accidents and that! I wondered if you remembered him being born because I simply wondered if you remembered who helped your moth
er then if she was laid up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Would you say your parents did have friends who weren't in any way connected by marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 They did have friends at all those homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Would you say that they were friends that they shared equally or would they be more friends your father made or your mother made?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I should think it would be joint.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And where did they see them? Take {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}, for example, where would they have seen their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well perhaps I'm g
oing on a little bit. You see, publicans were always friendly with one another. You see, and when beer was short, which it was at a certain time, they used to hold so much back and then they used to get together on Sunday night. You see I can remember goi
n
g down to a public house where the electricity showrooms are. It was kept by Mrs. Heritage, and we used to go down on a Sunday. And we used to go into Cornmarket to the Crown, and then over to Whites as well. You see, they was all in a little circle, you 
see, and there used to be one down on Highbridge Street that we'd go to on a Sunday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You'd go with your father would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Father and Mother. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, you'd all go together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what would you do, would you all sit and talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, this was when I was getting on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
But do you think that up to that 1918 period they themselves would have done this too, even though you, would, of course, have been too young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, I should say they would. They used to go 
out on a Sunday night, because you see you only had enough beer and that to supply for about two days, you see, two or three days, because the people used to make the rounds of the public houses as they got their share in, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And so you think that most of their friends were other publicans?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And these children that you used to play with, the lads in the area, you said their parents were friendly with your parents too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But they would have had other occupations also wouldn't they, or would they have been other publicans as well round there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Only one that was in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Plantation Road{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} at the Gardeners Arms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What was the occupation of the others? Do you remember their fathers' jobs?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. The only one that I can remember was the one that used to keep the Church Hall. He was a scout at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Christ{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Church{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. He was the caretaker, you see, of the Church Hall and he used to be a scout at Christ Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did your parents ever, do you remember them having people in for a meal, or in for tea, that sort of entertaining, you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember them being invited out on that sort of occasion, as people do today, or didn't it feature in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, there wasn't so much of that done as what there is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember friends calling in casually. Just calling round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Mostly on a Sunday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And would they have been offered some kind of refreshment then when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But it wouldn't have been an arranged meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That's what I was getting at.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, not an arranged thing, but if they dropped in they was quite welcome.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think your parents dropped in or called on people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not being in business, you wouldn't be able to you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You couldn't get away really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 They weren't musical, were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Not in making music and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think that when they got together with their friends they ever played any sorts of games at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 At Christmas time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes? What kind of games?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You know, at the festive season. Used to play cards and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But otherwise, would they not have played cards regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what about billiards? Were there billiards and that in a public house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
You mentioned last week that when you used to go carol singing you didn't sing outside because it was the upper class people who lived in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}North Oxford{\*\xmlclose}
. How, at that time, would you have seen the classes at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}? I mean the upper class living there...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Well, I should say round the Bardwell Road, Norham Road, and Norham Gardens and all round that way they were the upper class with servants. And all the big houses along the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}
Banbury Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} that had coachmen with their drays and their horses and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And how would you describe the other classes in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well there used to be the middle class and there used to be the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How would you describe the middle class as distinct from the upper class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well at that time in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 if people worked at college and that they was called the middle class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You mean the college staff?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 The college scouts and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And they considered themselves middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. They considered themselves middle class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think it was the distinction that they didn't do sort of heavy work? Was that it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes it was more like black coated work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And what other kinds of occupation would they have put in the middle class? What about school teachers and that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. Yes school teachers and any black coat worker I should say. Bank managers and so on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You'd put them in the middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But then, what were the occupations of the people in the upper classes at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well they was mostly retired. You know what I mean, they had plenty of money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well many of them, I suppose, never earned a penny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No they never earned a halfpenny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Would you have included some of the college tutors and fellows in that group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, that I wouldn't like to say, because I wouldn't know the earnings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Presumably some of them had private means and others didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Like it is today, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What about the doctors and people like that - did they live in the style of the upper class at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. They used to live in the upper class houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did all these people of all classes come into the public house? Do you remember the middle and upper classes coming in as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Only the middle and working class. You wouldn't get any of the upper class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you come into any personal contact with them at any time - besides the carol singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what group would you have said you yourself belonged to at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I should say the middle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you think your mother thought herself as belonging to the middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, she did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you think this was because of t
he work that your father did? Was this how she would have graded herself, or was it because of her own parents, or because of the kind of place she lived in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I should think, you see, that being in business she would naturally think she was middle class.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And your mother, how would she show respect then to the lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well she never used to see the lady much, you see, because you was right apart from them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You didn't cross paths anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember who, at th
at time, when you were at school you would have called 'sir' or 'madam'? What sort of people? Who would you have called 'sir'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well the school master and the teachers and anybody that you knew above your station in live.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Above your own station, yes. Not just any older person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Not just any older person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember people calling your father 'sir' because he was middle class and they were working class, say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You don't remember his being called 'sir'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Publicans are more treated in a matey sort of way aren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
And in that area, around where you were living, you were saying you know how you had the upper classes, the middle classes and the working classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Who were considered the most important people though, do you think? Could you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 The most important people of the three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well not }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 exactly}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664  of the three. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 The kind of people, well such as in a village you often feel that it's the vicar
, or perhaps the squire, who is considered to be the 'king pin', in a way. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I wondered if at that time there were people who stood out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember, was there a Chapel nearby where people went? Or did everyone go to the Church that you went to?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Always went to Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Always went to Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You don't remember Chapel goers among your acquaintance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Now, in the working class, would you say that those you knew in Oxford and round about, did they a
ll have the same standard of living, or would you say there were a lot of divisions among them, the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well it all depends where they worked because at that time wages weren't very high. You see, barring colleges and that, until the matte
r of 1914 you see, when there was the war on and they made munitions at Cowley and that, there was' hardly anything else, barring the Corporation and printing. Well the Clarendon Press was there, and the foundry. Jewis's foundry was there, but you see mos
t of it was in the shops.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So there were shop workers, many of whom got very little money, what class would you have put them in, because they were white?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, you see, they'd be the working class, wouldn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Well we say so today, but I just wondered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well they would be the working class then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Do you think, as you were saying earlier, that there were very few opportunities for them, but were there still quite a lot of differences, do you think, in the standards that they had of pay and living conditions within these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Yes I should say there was, because you see, you take the painting and decorating business, will you see during the winter it stopped, you see, and there was no dole at that time, you see, so there was a terrible pinch in a lot of places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think, at that time in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Oxford{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, do you think it was possible to move from one class to another? Do you remember anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No it wouldn't be easy at all. No, not at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Would it have been possible, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 It may have been possible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You don't remember people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But I don't remember anybody.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you think the same would have been when your father was at Kings Sutton and Hackney as well? She was in business 
there too, wasn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 She was in business there, too, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So the fact of her owning a public house didn't make any difference to how she would have seen herself in social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think your mother and father had the same attitude to people in different social classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well that I wouldn't like to say. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You don't remember from the way they treated people and behaved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. They was always polite as we were taught to be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 To everyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 To everyone, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
You don't remember then, a lot of people were at that time being brought up to treat some kinds of people differently from others, depending on their station in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you ever remember anybody touching caps and dropping curtsies and that sort of thing to your parents and other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I think it was more a country thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I think it was more country people. Of course when they was down at Kings Sutton you had to doff your hat to the Lady and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Your father did that, did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think that worried him at all, having to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 He took it for granted did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember people at that time using the phrase he's a 'real gentleman' or she's a 'real lady' about people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, you'd hear that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What do you think people would mean at that time when they used that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well they wouldn't be above talking to you or anything like that, you know. And asking you questions and that.
 I think a 'real gentleman' or a 'real lady' would do that sort of thing. You know, not be standoffish. They wouldn't be standoffish at all, they'd stop and speak.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So when people used it they referred to manners more than money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Manners more than money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Now, I went to ask you a bit about the police. Do you ever remember seeing policemen around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Frequently? Were they much around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Well I don't know whether I ought to tell you this or not, but they used to go to the porch of St. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 Bernard's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
 and St. James's every night and the runner from the police station would bring them coffee. And they would have their coffee in the porch of St. Bernard's and St. James's Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you think that they shouldn't have done that, do you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes. But there was always one or two of the coppers that liked a drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, and of course they aren't allowed to drink on duty are they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. But I've done many a time put two bottles of beer 
on the wall for them at night, you know. On our wall, and they used to come up the passage and have their drink there. And I know that I've done that hundreds of times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So how did you, yourself, feel about the police, I mean, do you know whether your 
mother said, same as many mothers did, that she'd call the police if you were naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You weren't brought up to think of them as people to be frightened of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember how you did think of the police? You're your attitude to them was when you were a lad?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Well they was all right. If you got into any scrapes, well they'd go round and give you a clip of the ear or something like that, and I think boys were all the better for it. I think it kept a lot of boys in order, that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Without things getting further?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How do you think they treated the people, you know, the adults sort of, round about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh, all right. They were just human beings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Now, who did the pub that your father ran belong to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Murrells?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 It was Murrells, yes. And did you ever see the Landlord, or it would have been an agent really, I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. I very often went and took the orders down to Murrells Brewery and see'd Mr. Murrell down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Mr. Murrell himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, down in the office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What sort of a man was he like to deal with? How did he strike you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Very nice. They used to live at Headington. Headington Hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And as a landlord your father didn't have any difficulties with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Do you ever remember, this way sound a foolish question to you, but do you ever remember thinking that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet at any time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Because from what you tell me they were better off than a lot of people, but you still think times were hard, were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, times were hard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Right through your childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And you were conscious of this then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did your parents talk about money and the difficulty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No they never used to talk about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What sort of ways do you think you were made conscious of the fact that it wasn't too plentiful?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, it was, they got by. That's about all I can say, if you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 That Saturday job that you had, for example, was that a sort of necessity really, or did you do it...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, I done it because to give me a little bit of pocket money and to help them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Had you for some reason or other not wanted to have it do you think they would have been upset?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No, I needn't have done it if I hadn't wanted to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Because in some families of course it was absolutely essential. You never needed, presumably, with the standard of living you had, you got by, you never needed help of any kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Now about school. How old were you when you first went to school in Hackney, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did you go from the age of five, right through into the afternoon, or did you come back at midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well I couldn't say that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. And what sort of school was that one - the Hackney one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Just an ordinary elementary school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Not Church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And mixed Infants would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. A mixed school right up 'til I came to Oxford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Were you really? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No divisions between the boys and the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And at this school in Hackney, I believe you said it was just at the end of the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Just across the road and along the end of the other road. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. So you went on your own did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
Well I wouldn't say I went on my own when I was five, I expect I went with my sister, because my sister went to the same school you see, to start off with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And what did you do about your midday meal, did you come home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well it was only five minutes walk so I came back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember at that school in Hackney what you thought about the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You don't remember anything in that way? Do you remember anything about the teachers, any particular teacher, or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember any punishments or how you were treated as far as discipline was concerned in Hackney?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well we used to get the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, or dunces can and stood in the corner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you ever get that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, I had it once or twice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what sort of things would you get the cane for? What type of offences?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well, for not doing your lessons, you know, and for acting the fool or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Fairly small things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And did the girls get it too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Would you say your parents showed an interest in your school work? I'm talking now over the whole period.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Over the whole?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, they used to. If you didn't take y
our report back to them they wanted to know what was the matter. You know, your reports always had to go to them and they saw that they had them. There was no tearing them up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Did you get reports at all your schools?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you ever remember, at Hackney, your mother or father visiting the school and meeting the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. There was no Parents Associations or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Not in those days, no, not that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 At Hackney do you remember anythin
g about the social backgrounds of the children. Did they come from homes similar to yours, or were there a lot of working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well it was mixed. It was mixed because mostly round Hackney at that time they was all working class people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. So you think there was a majority of working class children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember any distinctions being made by the teachers between the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And the children themselves, do you remember them being different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. You used to play with your own set of pals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And they could be from all walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 I think children make less of that sort of thing than grown ups, don't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Do you remember any gangs or groups in that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember any children who were a bit outcast? You sometimes find this in schools - left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. I don't think so. Through my school life I don't remember any children being outcasts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You don't remember any children for instance coming from a Work}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 h}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 ouse? Some children at that time used to come from a Work}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
ouse to school and were set apart.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14106629 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Sutton, that was much further away I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 How long did it take you to get to that one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Twenty minutes - half an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And would you walk there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Walk, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And what about your {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 12}}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}}midday{\*\xmlclose} meal then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Come home, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You came home to dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You walked a lot in your life didn't you! Were you pretty thin?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, I was. I had to walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember anything about that school? What it was like, or what your opinion was of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Well it was a mixed school and, of course, being in a village there wasn't many children. I should say at the most there was,
 what 80 or 90, at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Would that have been quite a bit smaller than the one in Hackney?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And I should say that there was, want, about four teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And what did you feel about school? Were you a child who dragged himself to school unwillingly, or did you...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh no. I used to go and we used to get through the lessons. Well as a matter of fact your school days were your best days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 You think so?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So you weren't a child who had any strong bitterness about school or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember, at King}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 s Sutton, that is, those teachers, what they emphasise as important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 The three 'R's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 The three 'R's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 They dinned that in did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 What about other things to do with behaviour, like manners and tidiness and punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Oh you had to be on time for school, else you used to have a red mark.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And things like the way you spoke and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And neatness, did they care about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And would you say there, was it similar to Hackney in that the children all mixed in without faction?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes, it was a mixed school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And quite an integrated school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And just to get on now to the last school in Oxford. You stayed all the time did you at St. Bernard and St. James?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And that was a boys school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 It was the first time you had been in just a boys school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did you notice any difference in being just at a boys school? Do you think it made any difference to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. It didn't make any difference. You just took it in your stride.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And there presumably you just walked, you lived near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And you came home to dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes I came home to dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And do you remember anything, you know, about that school particularly? Happy there were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Were there any particular teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 There used to be a Mr. Cox. Of course the Headmaster was Mr. Dent. We used to call him "gaffer". "Gaffer Dent".
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 But you didn't call him that to his face!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 He heard it once or twice and he gave the boys the caning for it. He's still alive. Yes he lives at Marston. I should say he i
s getting well over the 90s now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. Were you caned, you know, quite often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Would you say there was more caning there than at the other schools or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. I think Mr. Dent was the stricter of the lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes, of all your schools?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Was he a good teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. He was very good indeed. Very good.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And at that school were there also no contests between teachers and parents? Do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. Of course, mother and father knew Mr. Dent, and knew Mr. Cox as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Did they know them from being...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 From acquaintance, myself being at school, and my brother being at school, and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Where would they have actually met him do you think? They didn't go up to the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. If they ever met him in the street or that, you know, they'd have a chat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So there was contact with them in that kind of a way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 In that school was there also middle class children and working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 Yes. And what about children of upper class parents, were there any there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. They used to go to the High School. The one in George Street. You know, George Street, New In Hall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1272141\charrsid16135664  (?)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664  Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12265667\charrsid16135664 The boys' school, yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 
And were there any gangs or groups in that school, do you think, or children that...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No we never used to go in gangs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No. There weren't any at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16081106 HA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 So looking back on your school days, do you think most of your schools were contented communities really?
