\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3238463 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7084409\charrsid16135664 And if you'd had an opportunity, would you have continued your education do you think then?
